<HEAD>Anchorman d'Arvor, Live to Paris from Atlanta</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PARIS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   France's most-watched television network, TF1, says
it will broadcast its main evening newscast live from Atlanta on
